graph TB
    Start[User Opens Test Detail] --> Check{AI Analysis<br/>in Database?}

    Check -->|Yes| Display[Display Cached Analysis<br/>Root Cause<br/>Component<br/>Confidence<br/>Evidence<br/>Suggested Action]

    Check -->|No| CallAPI[Call /api/analyze-failure]

    CallAPI --> PrepareData[Prepare Data:<br/>- Test Name<br/>- Error Message<br/>- Build Logs last 3000 chars<br/>- Platform<br/>- Version]

    PrepareData --> VertexAI[Send to Vertex AI<br/>Claude Sonnet 4<br/>us-east5]

    VertexAI --> Analyze[Claude Analyzes Failure]

    Analyze --> Classify{Classify<br/>Failure Type}

    Classify --> ProductBug[Product Bug]
    Classify --> AutoBug[Automation Bug]
    Classify --> SysIssue[System Issue]
    Classify --> Transient[Transient]
    Classify --> Investigate[To Investigate]

    ProductBug --> Results[Generate Analysis:<br/>Root Cause<br/>Component<br/>Confidence 0-100%<br/>Evidence from logs<br/>Suggested Action]
    AutoBug --> Results
    SysIssue --> Results
    Transient --> Results
    Investigate --> Results

    Results --> SaveDB[(Save to Database<br/>ai_analyses table)]

    SaveDB --> Display

    Display --> End[User Reviews Analysis]

    Note1[Cost: ~$0.024 per analysis]
    Note2[Results cached permanently]

    style Check fill:#ffffcc
    style VertexAI fill:#ffccff
    style SaveDB fill:#99ccff
    style Display fill:#ccffcc
    style Classify fill:#ffffcc
